{{!< default}}

{{!--
    Element & typography test page ("kitchen sink") for building out the CSS.
    Plain semantic HTML so it doubles as a portable reference. Exactly ONE <h1>
    (the page title) to honour the accessibility baseline; the headings section
    below demonstrates h2–h6 as live headings.
--}}

<h1>Kitchen Sink — element &amp; typography test</h1>

<p>This page exists to exercise the stylesheet while it is being built. It
collects the common HTML elements on a single page so styling regressions are
easy to spot. It is not the real homepage.</p>

<p>A paragraph of <a href="#">inline elements</a> for testing runs of text:
<strong>strong importance</strong>, <b>bold</b>, <em>emphasis</em>, <i>italic</i>,
<u>underline</u>, <s>struck through</s>, <del>deleted</del> and <ins>inserted</ins>
text, <mark>highlighted</mark>, <small>small print</small>, H<sub>2</sub>O and
E=mc<sup>2</sup>, the abbreviation <abbr title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS</abbr>,
inline <code>code()</code>, the key <kbd>Esc</kbd>, sample output <samp>OK</samp>,
a variable <var>x</var>, a citation <cite>The Title</cite>, an inline quote
<q>quoted text</q>, a <dfn>definition</dfn> term, and a <time datetime="2026-06-11">date</time>.</p>


<div class=card>
<p>This is a card</p>
</div>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="headings-title">
    <h2 id="headings-title">Headings</h2>
    <p>The page <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> is at the top. Levels two through six:</p>
    <h2>Heading level 2</h2>
    <h3>Heading level 3</h3>
    <h4>Heading level 4</h4>
    <h5>Heading level 5</h5>
    <h6>Heading level 6</h6>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="text-title">
    <h2 id="text-title">Text blocks</h2>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod
    tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam,
    quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo
    consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse.</p>
    <p>Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia
    deserunt mollit anim id est laborum. <a href="#">A longer link inside a
    paragraph</a> to check wrapping and underline behaviour across line breaks.</p>

    <blockquote cite="https://example.com">
        <p>A blockquote: design is not just what it looks like and feels like.
        Design is how it works.</p>
        <footer>— <cite>Someone, somewhere</cite></footer>
    </blockquote>

    <figure>
        <blockquote>
            <p>A pull quote inside a figure, to test figure + blockquote
            together.</p>
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption>Attribution in a <code>figcaption</code></figcaption>
    </figure>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="lists-title">
    <h2 id="lists-title">Lists</h2>

    <h3>Unordered (nested)</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>First item</li>
        <li>Second item
            <ul>
                <li>Nested item</li>
                <li>Nested item
                    <ul>
                        <li>Deeply nested item</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Third item</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Ordered (nested)</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>First step</li>
        <li>Second step
            <ol>
                <li>Sub-step one</li>
                <li>Sub-step two</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Third step</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Description list</h3>
    <dl>
        <dt>Term</dt>
        <dd>Definition of the term.</dd>
        <dt>Another term</dt>
        <dd>Its definition.</dd>
        <dd>A second definition for the same term.</dd>
    </dl>

    <h3>Unstyled list (<code>role="list"</code>, bullets removed by the reset)</h3>
    <ul role="list">
        <li>No marker</li>
        <li>No marker</li>
        <li>No marker</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="table-title">
    <h2 id="table-title">Table</h2>
    <table>
        <caption>A table caption describing the data</caption>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th scope="col">Name</th>
                <th scope="col">Role</th>
                <th scope="col">Votes</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">Ada</th>
                <td>Engineer</td>
                <td>128</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">Grace</th>
                <td>Admiral</td>
                <td>256</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">Alan</th>
                <td>Mathematician</td>
                <td>512</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
        <tfoot>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row" colspan="2">Total</th>
                <td>896</td>
            </tr>
        </tfoot>
    </table>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="code-title">
    <h2 id="code-title">Preformatted &amp; code</h2>
    <pre><code>def greet(name: str) -&gt; str:
    """A preformatted code block to test monospace and overflow."""
    return f"Hello, {name}! This line is intentionally long to test horizontal scrolling behaviour."</code></pre>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="media-title">
    <h2 id="media-title">Media</h2>
    <figure>
        <img src="{{asset "img/placeholder.svg"}}" alt="A grey placeholder image, 640 by 360 pixels" width="640" height="360">
        <figcaption>An image inside a <code>figure</code> with a
        <code>figcaption</code>.</figcaption>
    </figure>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="forms-title">
    <h2 id="forms-title">Forms</h2>
    <form action="#" method="get">
        <fieldset>
            <legend>Text inputs</legend>
            <p>
                <label for="f-text">Text</label>
                <input type="text" id="f-text" name="f-text" placeholder="Type here…">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-email">Email (required)</label>
                <input type="email" id="f-email" name="f-email" required placeholder="you@example.com">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-password">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="f-password" name="f-password" autocomplete="new-password">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-search">Search</label>
                <input type="search" id="f-search" name="f-search">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-number">Number</label>
                <input type="number" id="f-number" name="f-number" min="0" max="10" step="1" value="3">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-url">URL (disabled)</label>
                <input type="url" id="f-url" name="f-url" value="https://example.com" disabled>
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-readonly">Read-only</label>
                <input type="text" id="f-readonly" name="f-readonly" value="Can't edit me" readonly>
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-list">With datalist</label>
                <input type="text" id="f-list" name="f-list" list="options">
                <datalist id="options">
                    <option value="Alpha"></option>
                    <option value="Beta"></option>
                    <option value="Gamma"></option>
                </datalist>
            </p>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>Date, range &amp; pickers</legend>
            <p>
                <label for="f-date">Date</label>
                <input type="date" id="f-date" name="f-date">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-time">Time</label>
                <input type="time" id="f-time" name="f-time">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-color">Colour</label>
                <input type="color" id="f-color" name="f-color" value="#1c64f2">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-range">Range</label>
                <input type="range" id="f-range" name="f-range" min="0" max="100" value="50">
            </p>
            <p>
                <label for="f-file">File</label>
                <input type="file" id="f-file" name="f-file">
            </p>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>Choices</legend>
            <p>
                <label for="f-select">Select</label>
                <select id="f-select" name="f-select">
                    <optgroup label="Group one">
                        <option>First</option>
                        <option>Second</option>
                    </optgroup>
                    <optgroup label="Group two">
                        <option>Third</option>
                        <option>Fourth</option>
                    </optgroup>
                </select>
            </p>

            <fieldset>
                <legend>Radio buttons</legend>
                <p>
                    <input type="radio" id="r1" name="radios" value="1" checked>
                    <label for="r1">Option one</label>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <input type="radio" id="r2" name="radios" value="2">
                    <label for="r2">Option two</label>
                </p>
            </fieldset>

            <fieldset>
                <legend>Checkboxes</legend>
                <p>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="c1" name="c1" checked>
                    <label for="c1">Checked</label>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="c2" name="c2">
                    <label for="c2">Unchecked</label>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <input type="checkbox" id="c3" name="c3" disabled>
                    <label for="c3">Disabled</label>
                </p>
            </fieldset>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>Textarea</legend>
            <p>
                <label for="f-textarea">Message</label>
                <textarea id="f-textarea" name="f-textarea" placeholder="A textarea with no rows attribute (min-height comes from the reset)."></textarea>
            </p>
        </fieldset>

        <p>
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            <button type="reset">Reset</button>
            <button type="button">Plain button</button>
            <button type="button" disabled>Disabled</button>
        </p>
    </form>
</section>

<hr>

<section aria-labelledby="interactive-title">
    <h2 id="interactive-title">Interactive &amp; status</h2>

    <details>
        <summary>A <code>details</code> / <code>summary</code> disclosure</summary>
        <p>Hidden content revealed on toggle — no JavaScript required.</p>
    </details>

    <p>
        <label for="f-progress">Progress</label>
        <progress id="f-progress" max="100" value="70">70%</progress>
    </p>
    <p>
        <label for="f-meter">Meter</label>
        <meter id="f-meter" min="0" max="100" low="33" high="66" optimum="90" value="80">80 out of 100</meter>
    </p>
</section>
